#3135
@@mRoot of the Heartspire@@n~
Root of the Heartspire lies steeped in bruise-colored lanternlight, its stones lacquered with soot and violet varnish.

Saintly effigies with broken eyes frame the passage while ravens scratching behind stone circles the chamber without a source.

A violet draft crawls over your skin like wet silk.
~
4 3
S
#3136
@@mCauseway of Converging Wings@@n~
Causeway of Converging Wings lies steeped in violet-black candlelight, its stones lacquered with soot and violet varnish.

The long approach channels pilgrims into a single file between watching statues.

Every breath fogs black before vanishing into the stone.
~
