#3137
@@mSanctum of the Ebon Pulse@@n~
Sanctum of the Ebon Pulse lies steeped in ink-violet moonshine, its stones lacquered with soot and violet varnish.

Prayer sigils burn in the stone as though etched by lightning and grief.

Somewhere nearby, chains tap a slow funeral rhythm.
~
