#3138
@@mThe Umbral Crownseat@@n~
The Umbral Crownseat lies steeped in cold plum fire, its stones lacquered with soot and violet varnish.

The crownseat rises above steps of onyx, surrounded by severed standards and votive skulls.

Your shadow stretches wrong, lagging half a heartbeat behind you.
~
